txt.en: 'Everyone that was missing has returned! Thank you, [placeholder]. My people are indebted to you for your aid.'\n\nLorndúr bows deeply.
Lorndúr can be found in Loeglond.\n\nYou should talk to Lorndúr.
Raft-elves from Loeglond are missing. Lorndúr believes they may be in great danger and would like you to go find them.
Injured Elves can be found along the Forest River between Felegoth and Loeglond.\n\nYou should heal injured Elves.
'I sent several of my raft-elves to go investigate the missing shipments from Felegoth, but they have not returned. I fear this is the work of Orcs. Please find them, and aid them if needed.'
